{"tid":2256364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"61歲宮崎美子性感月曆銷量勝《鬼滅》","createTime":"2020-10-24T09:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T11:06:08.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1c937db41402888b9debb663044a2fbe672ec040","tid":2256364,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"年屆61歲的日本女星宮崎美子為紀念入行40周年，推出性感月曆及純影集，以比堅尼泳裝上陣，由攝影大師篠山紀信操刀，本周一接受訂購後反應熱烈，宮崎獲讚身材白滑，絕不遜於後生女，成為網絡熱話之餘，更高踞當地各大購物網的銷量榜冠軍。觀乎日本Amazon月曆榜走勢，宮崎的新作雖然索價6,600日圓（約488港元），仍打敗熱爆動漫《鬼滅之刃》僅售1,980日圓（約146港元）的平價月曆，宮崎連日來登上銷量冠軍，被封為是《鬼滅之刃》唯一「剋星」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201024/JOST6PTQLNGO3D3WJJOTYUGZM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201024%2FJOST6PTQLNGO3D3WJJOTYUGZM4%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=6a773b5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201024%2FJOST6PTQLNGO3D3WJJOTYUGZM4%2F&h=ecb32288\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201024/JOST6PTQLNGO3D3WJJOTYUGZM4/</a>"},{"pid":"916c4af6c3fce4652537165befb8727063a6354f","tid":2256364,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7ZEyoMVoY7C78t67jIlBBPszPh8=/535x503/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HELQK43YRBEMNOVKRI4ZTYKICY.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ZEyoMVoY7C78t67jIlBBPszPh8%3D%2F535x503%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHELQK43YRBEMNOVKRI4ZTYKICY.jpg&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=1f31b011\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ZEyoMVoY7C78t67jIlBBPszPh8%3D%2F535x503%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-north